## Dynamic Fixtures

### Using Loops

```yaml
# test/fixtures/articles.yml

<% 20.times do |i| %>
bulk_<%= i %>:
  user: john
  title: Bulk Article <%= i %>
  slug: bulk-article-<%= i %>
  body: Body content for article <%= i %>
  status: published
  published_at: <%= i.days.ago %>
  views_count: <%= rand(100..1000) %>
  created_at: <%= (i + 1).days.ago %>
<% end %>
```

### Conditional Content

```yaml
# test/fixtures/users.yml

<% 5.times do |i| %>
user_<%= i %>:
  email: user<%= i %>@example.com
  password_digest: <%= BCrypt::Password.create('password') %>
  first_name: User<%= i %>
  last_name: Test
  admin: <%= i == 0 %>
  active: <%= i.even? %>
  created_at: <%= i.weeks.ago %>
<% end %>
```

